{"tid":712394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 拖欠半年薪金 逾10工人北角衝馬路追薪","createTime":"2018-06-22T05:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T10:20:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0c393e891043ece922878b7f3aa44de59f04ef","tid":712394,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:12:24.000Z","msg":"北角英皇道338號一幢商廈對開，早上9時許，17名負責水務工程的工人，包括16男1女聲稱被拖欠薪金，聯袂到上址擬向判頭所屬的公司，追討欠薪，並且拉起橫額抗議。現場消息稱，期間有工人一度衝出馬路，警方接報到場勸喻後，工人返回安全位置，資方正派出代表到場了解。<br />\n<br />\n據工人稱，他們開工的地點分別位於荃灣及青衣，部分人<span style=\"color: red;\">遭拖欠近半年的薪金</span>，涉款近250萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180622/photo/bkn-20180622100600690-0622_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180622113049\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180622%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180622100600690-0622_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180622113049&h=42000332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180622/bkn-20180622100600690-0622_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180622%2Fbkn-20180622100600690-0622_00822_001.html&d=%2BRw2xM0Hd4f155oiEcL3Q8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e52e6693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180622/bkn-20180622100600690-0622_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5fd039d5babf26d36b5ac3c795ad901e869c6e5b","tid":712394,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"返工=賭搏(唔知有冇糧出)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac36447b4b305cc6879995e26783711f73d94441","tid":712394,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/011226_eba6400fe2bfe149f90560d62bc89cd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F